        "gg-dZbzIeuj_text": "<p>The tank is crafted from <strong>57% Polyamide and 43% Elastane</strong>, a high-performance blend selected for its softness, breathability, and stretch.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The fabric moves naturally with your body while <strong>maintaining its shape and support</strong> throughout the day. Smooth and lightweight against the skin, it feels comfortable to wear for hours without restriction.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Care Instructions</strong><br>To preserve the fabric’s quality and elasticity:</p><ul><li>Wash at temperatures below 40°C</li><li>Do not bleach</li><li>Do not iron</li><li>Do not dry clean</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Designed for everyday wear, with long-lasting comfort and durability.</p>",
        "gg0kqiBWosj_text": "<p><strong>I Didn’t Think I’d Ever See This Lift Again</strong></p>",
        "gg1-ZKocESm_text": "<p>I stopped wearing bras at home &nbsp;and honestly, most days altogether. This tank gives enough support to feel secure without squeezing or digging in. I forget I’m wearing it.</p>",
        "gg21WCNBJX4_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg56Y3gCxIT_text": "<p>I honestly thought I’d never see my chest look like this again. It feels lifted, supported, and natural — like my body in my 20s, but comfortable.</p>",
        "ggDWQKfSkTu_text": "<p>Karine N.</p>",
        "ggEXlXo6pOb_text": "<p>Meggy J.</p>",
        "ggFJ-UJ9nnJ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggHI6suLSFf_text": "<p>Even my basic jeans + tee outfits look more flattering. My waist looks more defined and my top sits so much nicer on my body.</p>",
        "ggHaLbhbPo4_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>Estimated Delivery Times:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>UK &amp; EU:</strong>&nbsp;8-12 business days&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>US &amp; Canada:</strong>&nbsp;4 to 12 business days</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>Rest of the World:</strong>&nbsp;8-15 business days&nbsp;</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>- 90-Day Return Window</strong>: If you’re still unsatisfied, you may return your item within 45 days of delivery for a refund.</span><br><br><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><strong>- Money-Back Guarantee</strong>: Once we receive the returned item in its original condition, we’ll process your refund.</span></li></ul>",
        "ggIecaXd1H7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggLQJTpP6k4_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggORXewsPBB_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggOZcvbrPRE_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_554576614113936244-936f659e-1f7e-4287-ac81-ff34c91d32f6.svg",
        "ggRcFobOsyx_text": "<p>This is what I wanted shapewear to be.</p>",
        "ggV66t7CVol_childItem_0": "<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Materials &amp; Care</span></p>",
        "ggV66t7CVol_childItem_1": "<p><strong>&nbsp;FREE RETURNS &amp; Exchanges</strong></p>",
        "ggVQb5cCw_c_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggX50r-F1f3_text": "<p>Olivia J.</p>",
        "ggZYfcGr3Ek_text": "<p>Jade K.</p>",
        "gg_RjLn1yIv_text": "<p>Marta C.</p>",
        "gga9ifit7kz_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggaR7iD5kxy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggdNAueEkoC_text": "<p><strong>Finally Real Support — Without a Bra</strong></p>",
        "ggfXjbVnKDf_text": "<p>Most shapewear made me look weird or created bulges. Elōa just makes my silhouette look clean and natural, like my body but upgraded.</p>",
        "ggggrwoLGS__text": "<p>Margot H.</p>",
        "ggi2_S5dYAi_text": "<p>I look better in EVERY outfit now.</p>",
        "ggiqGqP7jVp_text": "<p>My Tops Finally Fit Right</p>",
        "gglbb0LRzeD_text": "<p>Rated <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong>4.7</strong></span>/ 5 based on <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong><u>1897 Reviews.</u></strong></span></p>",
        "ggmzLhi-ljn_childItem_0": "<p>reviews</p>",
        "ggt81-6qRlx_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggui3ncSB5m_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggvOm1GF6hu_text": "<p>Soft fabric, great fit, and no wires. My shoulders feel better and my tops finally sit right. Definitely buying more.</p>",
        "ggwea36gd3F_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggyWML2cdgn_text": "<p>After kids and time, I had accepted that my chest would never look the same. This tank made me feel confident again. I didn’t think a simple top could do that.</p>",
        "ggyt55QNeyn_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggzMRLKssKK_text": "<p><strong>It Gave Me My Confidence Back</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-603786005127889823"
    },
