        "ggMiRCe5hBz_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">“Built-in support that actually works.</span><br><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Lifted bust, smoother fit, and a cleaner silhouette under clothes.”</span></p>",
