        "ggYSoxxmRYH_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">“Out of all the built-in bra tank tops we tested, none offered support like this one.</span><br><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">It’s the fastest ‘bra-off to supported’ feeling we’ve experienced.”</span></p>",
