        "gg5mzVQA---_text": "<p>✅ <span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>Built-In Breast Support — Without a Bra</strong></span></p><p>This tank top is designed to <strong>support your breasts naturally</strong> — no underwire, no digging straps, no bulky bra layers.</p><p>A structured inner support gently holds the bust in place, helping prevent sagging while maintaining a soft, natural shape.</p><p>No squeezing.<br>No flattening.<br>No “shelf bra” feeling.</p><p>Just real support you can wear all day — comfortably.</p>",
