        "ggkmxagkbJY_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>💖 Smooth Silhouette. No Uniboob. Real Confidence.</strong></span></p><p>Unlike most built-in bra tanks that flatten the chest or create a “uniboob” effect, this design <strong>supports and separates the bust subtly</strong>, keeping a feminine, natural look.</p><p>No sagging</p><p>No shifting pads</p><p>No awkward lines under clothes</p><p>A supported chest changes everything:<br>how your tops fit, how you stand, and how you feel.</p><p>You move freely.<br>You feel supported.<br>You feel confident — all day long.</p>",
